## MotionDetect

###### Description

Primitive motion detector based on subtraction
 of frames.

###### Params

| Param | Type | Description |
| --- | --- | --- |
|**tCurr**|<var>[Tensor](/docs/tensor#Tensor)</var>|Current frame.|
|**tPrev**|<var>[Tensor](/docs/tensor#Tensor)</var>|Previous frame.|

###### Example

```js
gm.motionDetect(currentImage, previousImage);
```
